item.description:
Let's get together and dance to this great rock band!

I suggest we get there early because the place gets packed with this band.

I'm going to get there for 7:30 for some supper as well.

cell: 978-340-3381.  Please only use it on the day of the event.  You can email me with any questions before then.

Hope to see you there!

No need to rsvp no.
